<plot>What would you do if you could change everything in an instant? Nine year old Colin (Jason Armada) is faced with this question after discovering he has the terrifying power to erase anything he sees. Armed with a pad of paper, his skillful hand, and worst of all, his eraser, Colin sets off on a haunting journey though the depths of his own imagination to bring his every desire to reality. Join Colin as he learns the truth about our thoughts, and the dangers of the choices we make.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?142963</url></doc>
